  "text": "Despite not finding a relationship between SR and soil losses, a negative and weak correlation between SR and soil erodibility (K factor) can be noticed (Table 3) . For kaolinitic soils (1:1 minerals), the trend between soil loss and SR was not as significant; furthermore, soil loss was more related to clay dispersibility [CITATION_1] , whereas, the same authors reported a linear relationship for soils with 2:1 clay minerals.",
